  <project_license>MIT</project_license>

  <description>
    <p>TuxScale is a free and open source AI-powered video upscaler for Linux. It utilizes Real-ESRGAN models and Vulkan compute to enhance video quality locally.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>AI Frame Upscaling — Extracts video frames and upscales each one using Real-ESRGAN</li>
      <li>Desktop UI — Clean Electron + React interface for easy operation</li>
      <li>Batch Processing — Handle entire videos in one go</li>
      <li>Linux Native — Built and packaged for Linux</li>
      <li>Self-Contained — Backend binary and models are bundled with the app</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

